Map.Description: This conversion map reads 2.x FA **LOAD documents and generates FA 3.x documents in sysmanutil format. Modifications Mar 08 2011 res Per CSG Issue # ISS00055830, set ACQDSP_CD to null Jan 28 2011 res 3.9 ... Add bunch of stuff

Action.name: Execute
Action.Parameter:
linenumber = linenumber + 1 documentId = documentId + 1
if(linenumber >200) or pre_fa_num <> trim(Records("R1").Fields("FIXED-ASSET-NUMBER")) then write_hdr = 1 linenumber = 1 pre_fa_num = trim(Records("R1").Fields("FIXED-ASSET-NUMBER")) SequenceNumber = SequenceNumber + 1 else write_hdr = 0 end if

Action.name: Execute

MapExpressions.MapExpression: Dim sTextLine sTextline= DateConvert("yyyy/mm/dd","yyyy-mm-dd", Date())& " " & Time()&".000000" sTextLine

dim testline 'if len(trim(Records("FA-DOCH").Fields("ACQUISITION-METHOD"))) > 0 then ' testline = "<![CDATA[" & trim(Records("FA-DOCH").Fields("ACQUISITION-METHOD")) & "\U+005d]>" 'else 'ISS00055830 testline = "<![CDATA[1" & "\U+005d]>" testline = "<![CDATA[null" & "\U+005d]>" 'end if testline

DIM testdate if month(date()) = 7 then testdate = 1 elseif month(date()) = 8 then testdate = 2 elseif month(date()) = 9 then testdate = 3 elseif month(date()) = 10 then testdate = 4 elseif month(date()) = 11 then testdate = 5 elseif month(date()) = 12 then testdate = 6 elseif month(date()) = 1 then testdate = 7 elseif month(date()) = 2 then testdate = 8 elseif month(date()) = 3 then testdate = 9 elseif month(date()) = 4 then testdate = 10 elseif month(date()) = 5 then testdate = 11 elseif month(date()) = 6 then testdate = 12 end if
"<![CDATA[" & testdate & "\U+005d]>"

dim testline if len(trim(Records("FA-DOCD").Fields("ASSET-VALUE-1"))) = 0 then testline ="<![CDATA[null" & "\U+005d]>" else testline ="<![CDATA[" & rtrim(Records("FA-DOCD").Fields("ASSET-VALUE-1")) & "\U+005d]>" end if testline

DIM testdate if month(date()) = 7 or month(date()) = 8 or month(date()) = 9 then testdate = 1 elseif month(date()) = 10 or month(date()) = 11 or month(date()) = 12 then testdate = 2 elseif month(date()) = 1 or month(date()) = 2 or month(date()) = 3 then testdate = 3 elseif month(date()) = 4 or month(date()) = 5 or month(date()) = 6 then testdate = 4 end if
"<![CDATA[" & testdate & "\U+005d]>"

dim testline 'if len(trim(Records("FA-DOCH").Fields("FUND"))) > 0 then ' testline = "<![CDATA[" & rtrim(Records("FA-DOCH").Fields("FUND")) & "\U+005d]>" 'else testline = "<![CDATA[null" & "\U+005d]>" 'end if testline

dim testline 'if len(trim(Records("FA-DOCH").Fields("FUND"))) > 0 then ' testline = "<![CDATA[" & rtrim(Records("FA-DOCH").Fields("FUND")) & "\U+005d]>" 'else testline = "<![CDATA[null" & "\U+005d]>" 'end if testline

dim testline 'if len(trim(Records("FA-DOCH").Fields("FIXED-ASSET-TYPE"))) > 0 then ' testline = "<![CDATA[" & rtrim(Records("FA-DOCH").Fields("FIXED-ASSET-TYPE")) & "\U+005d]>" 'else testline = "<![CDATA[null" & "\U+005d]>" 'end if testline

dim testline 'if len(trim(Records("FA-DOCH").Fields("FA-GROUP"))) > 0 then ' testline = "<![CDATA[" & rtrim(Records("FA-DOCH").Fields("FA-GROUP")) & "\U+005d]>" 'else testline = "<![CDATA[null" & "\U+005d]>" 'end if testline

dim testline 'if len(trim(Records("FA-DOCD").Fields("ASSET-VALUE-1"))) > 0 then ' testline ="<![CDATA[" & rtrim(Records("FA-DOCD").Fields("ASSET-VALUE-1")) & "\U+005d]>" 'else testline ="<![CDATA[null" & "\U+005d]>" 'end if testline
